display_name: Apnea-Hypopnea Index (NREM): Apneas with >= 5% oxygen desaturation and with or without arousal+ hypopneas with > 30% flow reduction and with >= 5% oxygen desaturation and with or without arousal / hour of NREM sleep from type II polysomnography
calculation: 60 * ( hnrbp5 + hnrop5 + canbp5 + canop5 + oanbp5 + oanop5 ) / ( slpprdp - minremp )
